column2: SELECT TOP #  a.apogee_id,cast(str(a.glon,#,#) as float) glon,cast(str(a.glat,#,#) as float) glat,a.snr,a.vhelio_avg,a.vscatter,q.teff,q.logg,q.m_h,q.alpha_m,a.gaia_parallax,a.gaia_parallax_error,a.gaia_phot_bp_mean_mag,a.gaia_phot_g_mean_mag,a.gaia_phot_rp_mean_mag,a.gaia_pmdec,a.gaia_pmdec_error,a.gaia_pmra,a.gaia_pmra_error,a.gaia_r_est,a.gaia_r_hi,a.gaia_r_lo,a.gaia_radial_velocity,a.gaia_radial_velocity_error,a.max_h,a.max_jk,a.min_h,a.min_jk,a.nvisits,a.starflag,a.survey,a.target_id,a.telescope,a.verr,a.verr_med,o.j,o.h,o.k  FROM apogeeStar as a  JOIN apogeeObject as o ON a.apogee_id=o.apogee_id  JOIN aspcapStar as q ON a.apstar_id=q.apstar_id
